title: Bucks Control Game 1 in Boston | Weekends with Wos
description:
Wosny Lambre is joined by J. Kyle Mann to discuss the Bucks' impressive Game 1 victory in Boston (2:28). Then, they discuss what direction the Utah Jazz should go in this offseason (25:28).

Host: Wosny Lambre
Guest: J. Kyle Mann
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
